{"tid":2012144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再講一次  哨兵好重要","createTime":"2020-05-11T12:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T15:39:17.000Z","uid":282534,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1535cebaa212d0703fd56493bae9c73370d1f46f","tid":2012144,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"琴晚發生咩事 相信大家都知<br />\n但的確唔可以逃避問題<br />\n今次呢度唔講太多廢話 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 哨頻</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各大TG channel 早係危機之前十幾分鐘已發出通知 </span></strong><br />\n呢度就以我channel 為例 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDJt9PQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDJt9PQ.png&h=e6955a2d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzv00Wv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqzv00Wv.png&h=280aadcf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n早係狗方準備調兵時 已經睇到最新動向 同狗方離奇多次原地高舉藍旗<br />\n已經係一種signal   <br />\n而當各大TG channel 均同步地發出危險訊號時  <br />\n其實已經到左非常危急既地步  <br />\n因為往往資料去到哨頻時都須要時間  再報出黎俾大家睇已經係遲左2-3分鐘<br />\n所以往後如果各大TG Channel 同步發出危險訊號時  請開始準備撤退<br />\n加上現場多次缺乏哨兵同現場傳哨兵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令現場資詢陷於一種疲乏狀態</span>  <br />\n令現場人士既判斷能力進一步下降<br />\n要知道係戰場上 情報優先者永遠處於有利位置<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2. 自我意識不足</strong></span><br />\n大家落場永遠好似唔會定自己既行動去到邊個位/幾時/咩位就要散水<br />\n由於自己無制定撤退時間 <br />\n又基於齊上齊落原則 於是<span style=\"color: red;\">不斷reloop 你唔走我唔走</span><br />\n再睇返琴晚  其實係九點 十點打後 已經少左好多人流 <br />\n係少左大量唔係行動手足既掩護同緩衝既時候 行動就進入好危險既地步<br />\n要知道 越夜越少人  就越大自己人被捕既危險<br />\n基於目前狗方出手開始有選擇到目的地減少影響其他非示威者既手段 <br />\n上年既原則已經唔岩用  要UPDATE啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 哨兵不足  </span></strong><br />\n關於呢點  其實自10月同11月打後  <br />\n哨兵已經少左接近一半或以上既人<br />\n要知道哨兵  係情報入面係最最最重要既一環  <br />\n無左哨兵 地圖師同哨頻就好似無左對眼咁<br />\n所以不論你咩身份都好  做緊咩行動都好  <br />\n得閒你就幫手報哨啦  <br />\n<br />\n暫時講住咁多問題先  大家都須要時間消化一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度有個非常重要既事  就係 <br />\n重新使用 Telegram  因為打緊仗時只有telegram會有最新既資詢同資料<br />\n<br />\n我都明白大家諗 telegram 好多谷同好多公海好多msg好煩又好似好多鬼咁  <br />\n所以呢度我地只推薦大家如果岩岩用 telegram  只follow 大人數既channel 就OK啦<br />\n其他既 一步步黎   D咩公海谷地區谷 其實太多了  <br />\n而且最近風氣唔太好就唔建議大家入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有如果縑煩係可以Mute左個谷同channel 既notice </span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好因為咁而唔用telegram <br />\n<br />\n呢度放出我個人比較推薦新手/岩岩使用telegram既人follow既channel  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n氣象巴打⚠️ -  <a href=\"http://t.me/weatherjj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=cd71334c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/weatherjj</a><br />\nThe Watcher 狩望者哨兵頻道 - <a href=\"http://t.me/The_watcher_channel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FThe_watcher_channel&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=6b7e80a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/The_watcher_channel</a><br />\n糖水Channel -  <a href=\"http://t.me/eatsyrup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Featsyrup&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=aad0bb49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/eatsyrup</a><br />\n銀河系哨俠頻道 -  <a href=\"http://t.me/universalsentinelsinblack\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Funiversalsentinelsinblack&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=b0175c84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/universalsentinelsinblack</a><br />\n龍中哨channel - <a href=\"http://t.me/klsinglennonwall\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fklsinglennonwall&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=1f9beeca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/klsinglennonwall</a><br />\n抗爭行動交通頻道 -  <a href=\"http://t.me/ncetransport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fncetransport&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=d28de946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ncetransport</a><br />\n<br />\n至於我條channel 因為並唔係專一只做某方向既事 太雜亂 就唔推薦岩岩用既人follow <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外  我地黎緊會推出哨兵入門級教學 以及會招募哨兵  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家會幫幫忙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0996e28fa09738b3bbf439fd1af542f30953c3","tid":2012144,"uid":125502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"5b9e4b9595e31d458f4f5897760a8ef8d00fb526","tid":2012144,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80f1b20b787e708ebafbf07b26ca1f68d2639f8e","tid":2012144,"uid":260578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1535cebaa212d0703fd56493bae9c73370d1f46f","tid":2012144,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"琴晚發生咩事 相信大家都知<br />\n但的確唔可以逃避問題<br />\n今次呢度唔講太多廢話 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 哨頻</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各大TG channel 早係危機之前十幾分鐘已發出通知 </span></strong><br />\n呢度就以我channel 為例 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDJt9PQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDJt9PQ.png&h=e6955a2d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzv00Wv.png\" data-th